<div id="banner">
	<h1>segway report</h1>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p>I am writing this on <a href="http://www.segway.com/">a Segway</a>!</p>

<p>A friend of ours bought a Segway and entered the Early Delivery contest. He got the second one. He&#8217;s going away for the week so he&#8217;s letting us borrow it during that time.</p>

<p>It&#8217;s <em>so</em> awesome! We&#8217;ve been riding it all over &#8212; it&#8217;s so much fun. We have it for the week, so I&#8217;m happy to answer questions or take movies or whatever people want. <a href="mailto:segway@aaronsw.com">Send me an email.</a></p>

<p class="posted">posted December 22, 2002 04:36 PM (<a class="category" href="cat_personal">Personal</a>)  <a href="000771" rel="bookmark">#</a></p>
</div>

